  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and short first person horror. Your task is to find ghosts in werehause. Most of the time you have to walk and explore the warehouse but be careful because you never know what's around the corner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Max. You are a YouTuber who records \"haunted\" places. You are going to the warehouse in Glinojeck, where a tragedy once happened...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849700/extras/72edbc1d7bc8b54d650c1b41da1974c0.avif?t=1733072204\" width=718 height=548 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's better to play on headphones, because it's a horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game lasts half an hour.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and short first person horror. Your task is to find ghosts in werehause. Most of the time you have to walk and explore the warehouse but be careful because you never know what's around the corner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Max. You are a YouTuber who records \"haunted\" places. You are going to the warehouse in Glinojeck, where a tragedy once happened...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2849700/extras/72edbc1d7bc8b54d650c1b41da1974c0.avif?t=1733072204\" width=718 height=548 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's better to play on headphones, because it's a horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game lasts half an hour.</p>",
